<title><![CDATA[This Valentine’s Day (Feb. 12), Blind Date Live and Tiki Easy ...]]></title>
<link>https://imginn.com/p/DFkz5sPJgtI/</link>
<guid>https://imginn.com/p/DFkz5sPJgtI/</guid>
<description>
<![CDATA[<a href="https://instagram.com/p/DFkz5sPJgtI/">View on Instagram</a><p><img src="https://scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/475974991_4065697547034566_4360684852577303208_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2AF3htdRb00yC2vCq4ZqruoP73Snq2gLGkerIX04nstsDBD5Lui6Bmss4K1dDUA8hT8&_nc_ohc=ZX2CGGNM8BIQ7kNvgHWe-X8&_nc_gid=26d535cb18c1400db2aff005a2d0cc74&edm=AGenrX8BAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AYEpC7nLxaDPbwepHRQqL3C5r4Afd6Jc4N1wLJFR80152Q&oe=67D436B3&_nc_sid=ed990e" /><br>This Valentine’s Day (Feb. 12), Blind Date Live and Tiki Easy are teaming up to bring Asheville a FREE singles mixer like no other. You’ve heard of Blind Date Live… but what about Half-Blind Date Live?Here’s how it works: Three brave, pre-selected singles will be blindfolded and go on a real first date—live on stage—with a lucky, willing participant from the crowd. Think romance, chaos, and possibly some light panic. What could go wrong?Not single? No problem. The entertainment alone is worth it—witness chemistry in real-time, whether it’s instant sparks or a train wreck you can’t look away from. And if a couple actually wants to see each other again, a local sponsor will cover their second date. (Because nothing says romance like corporate funding.)Expect hilarity, unexpected connections, and plenty of liquid courage—whether it’s a tropical cocktail or a mocktail, Tiki Easy’s got you covered.So laugh. Drink. Fall in love. Or just judge other people’s love lives for sport.📍 Where: Asheville’s coolest speakeasy, Tiki Easy📅 When: Wednesday, February 12 at 7 PM💸 Cost: Absolutely FREEJust show up. No tickets, no pressure—unless you’re the one getting blindfolded. See you there!#tiki #asheville #datenight #bar #shoplocal]]>
</description>
<pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 23:00:30 -0500</pubDate>
</item>
